				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Impromptu Q&A With Rytan.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Xalmat: Any chance we can see many of our item summons go targetable?
<br />
Rytan: I'm all for it if I get some code support for a toggle that lets you deny incoming items
<br />

<br />
Xalmat: What do you think of the idea of swarm pets as spells? Redorious brought up the idea.
<br />
Rytan: I've thought about it before, but I like those restricted to AAs for the moment to keep them special
<br />

<br />
Xalmat: What about defensive/offensive discs for pets?
<br />
Rytan: Knights would burn my house down.
<br />

<br />
Xalmat: Curious, have you given thought to a concussion-like spell for magicians?
<br />
Rytan: Thought about it, but not convinced it's needed. 
<br />

<br />
Xalmat: There gonna be a possibility of an upgraded mod rod in omens?
<br />
Rytan: Doubtful
<br />

<br />

<br />
So there you have it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=204546" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Xalmat Lunaire</a> - <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Magician's Tower</a> - <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/viewforum.php?f=9" target="_blank" class="postlink">Lead Librarian</a>
